222
00:39:00,039 --> 00:39:11,039
 In terms of the company's upbringing, it can be said that it returned to its origins in a sense, which is a consensus obtained by those who aimed for it as "it must be different."

223
00:39:12,039 --> 00:39:31,039
 Why is it that even with the possibility of business withdrawal, they are able to continue growing?

224
00:39:31,039 --> 00:39:38,039
 What are the strengths of this long-established company?

225
00:39:39,039 --> 00:39:43,039
 Kao has many products that hold the top market share in various areas.

226
00:39:43,039 --> 00:39:50,039
 Laundry detergent has more than 40% share, bleach has more than 70%, they have not given up their long-held positions for many years.

227
00:39:50,039 --> 00:39:59,039
 Kao has been conducting research on removing stains since its establishment.

228
00:40:04,039 --> 00:40:11,039
 Every day, employees collect shirt collars and repeat detergent cleansing power tests.

229
00:40:11,039 --> 00:40:22,039
 They cut them in half and compare how much the stain removal differs between the new detergent and the previous one.

230
00:40:22,039 --> 00:40:31,039
