234
00:41:01,039 --> 00:41:11,039
 In 1995, they increased the power to remove yellowing from clothes using an enzyme called alkaline cellulase.

235
00:41:11,039 --> 00:41:23,039
 It took eight years to discover this enzyme that removes yellowing.

236
00:41:26,039 --> 00:41:31,039
 In 2001, they introduced air into the particles of the detergent. The particles burst in the water, dissolving faster and increasing cleaning power.

237
00:41:31,039 --> 00:41:46,039
